{%- comment -%}
/**
 * Dynamic Promo Blocks Component
 * 
 * A comprehensive promotional blocks section that creates flexible marketing layouts
 * with configurable modules supporting multi-language content, responsive design,
 * and customizable styling options.
 * 
 * CORE FEATURES:
 * • Multi-module layout (1 large left module + 3 smaller right modules)
 * • Responsive design with separate desktop and mobile configurations
 * • Multi-language support (EN, DE, FR, FI)
 * • Customizable background images and colors
 * • Flexible content positioning
 * • Configurable typography and button styling
 * • Touch-friendly mobile interface
 * • SEO-optimized structure
 * 
 * TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:
 * • CSS Grid layout for responsive module arrangement
 * • CSS custom properties for dynamic styling
 * • Liquid templating for multi-language content
 * • Responsive breakpoints at 768px and 890px
 * • Background image optimization for different screen sizes
 * • Flexible content positioning system
 * 
 * SHOPIFY INTEGRATION:
 * • Section schema with comprehensive settings
 * • Multi-language field support
 * • Image picker integration
 * • Color picker integration
 * • URL picker for button links
 * • Range sliders for sizing controls
 * 
 * RELATED FILES:
 * • sections/dynamic-Promo-Blocks.liquid (this file)
 * • layout/theme.liquid (main theme layout)
 * • templates/index.json (homepage template configuration)
 * • templates/index.context.finland.json (Finland market context)
 * 
 * RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS:
 * • Desktop: > 890px (full grid layout)
 * • Tablet: 768px - 890px (adjusted spacing)
 * • Mobile: < 768px (stacked layout, optimized images)
 * 
 * MODULE CONFIGURATION:
 * • Left Module: Large promotional area with background image
 * • Right Module 1: Smaller promotional block
 * • Right Module 2: Medium promotional block
 * • Right Module 3: Small promotional block
 * 
 * MULTI-LANGUAGE SUPPORT:
 * • English (default)
 * • German (DE)
 * • French (FR)
 * • Finnish (FI)
 * • Automatic locale detection and content switching
 * 
 * BROWSER COMPATIBILITY:
 * • Modern browsers with CSS Grid support
 * • Fallback layouts for older browsers
 * • Touch event support for mobile devices
 * 
 * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
 * • Optimized CSS with minimal specificity
 * • Efficient image loading with responsive images
 * • Minimal JavaScript dependencies
 * • CSS custom properties for dynamic theming
 * 
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * • Semantic HTML structure
 * • Proper heading hierarchy
 * • Keyboard navigation support
 * • Screen reader friendly content
 * • High contrast color options
 * 
 * CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
 * • Module heights (desktop and mobile)
 * • Background images and colors
 * • Content positioning (9-point grid system)
 * • Typography sizing and colors
 * • Button styling and colors
 * • Background image sizing and positioning
 * 
 * CONTENT MANAGEMENT:
 * • Visual section editor in Shopify admin
 * • Real-time preview capabilities
 * • Bulk content management
 * • Template inheritance support
 * 
 * USE CASES:
 * • Homepage promotional sections
 * • Product category highlights
 * • Seasonal campaign displays
 * • Brand storytelling layouts
 * • Call-to-action sections
 * • Multi-product showcases
 */
